y-plugin` and `agentcube-sdk` dependency pins | New |\n28: | `integrations/dify-plugin/GUIDE.md` | Plugin usage guide | New |\n29: | `integrations/dify-plugin/README.md` | Plugin documentation | New |\n30: | `integrations/dify-plugin/PRIVACY.md` | Plugin privacy policy | New |\n31: | `integrations/dify-plugin/.difyignore` | Dify ignore file | New |\n32: | `integrations/dify-plugin/icon.png` | Plugin icon (light) | New |\n33: | `integrations/dify-plugin/icon-dark.png` | Plugin icon (dark) | New |\n34: | `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` | FastAPI app with agents and sandbox runner | New |\n35: | `example/pcap-analyzer/requirements.txt` | FastAPI and LangChain dependencies | New |\n36: | `example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile` | Container image definition | New |\n37: | `example/pcap-analyzer/deployment.yaml` | Kubernetes deployment manifest | New |\n38: | `example/pcap-analyzer/README.md` | Analyzer documentation | New |\n39: \n40: ---\n41: \n42: ## Files to Modify\n43: \n44: | Path | Description | Change Type |\n45: |------|-------------|-------------|\n46: | | | |\n47: \n48: ---\n49: \n50: ## Files to Delete\n51: \n52: | Path | Description |\n53: |------|-------------|\n54: | | |\n55: \n56: ---\n57: \n58: ## Requirements\n59: \n60: ### AR-036-001: Dify Plugin Package Structure\n61: \n62: The system SHALL provide a complete Dify plugin package with all required files for plugin discovery and execution.\n63: \n64: #### Scenario: AR-036-001-A — Plugin package contains required files\n65: \n66: - **GIVEN** the plugin package root directory at `integrations/dify-plugin/`\n67: - **WHEN** the directory is inspected for file presence\n68: - **THEN** it SHALL contain `main.py`, `manifest.yaml`, `provider/agentcube.yaml`, `provider/agentcube.py`, `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml`, `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py`, `requirements.txt`, and optional documentation files (`GUIDE.md`, `README.md`, `PRIVACY.md`, `.difyignore`)\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: AR-036-001-B — Plugin entry point executes framework runner\n71: \n72: - **GIVEN** `main.py` is defined as the plugin entry point\n73: - **WHEN** the plugin process starts via the manifest-declared entrypoint\n74: - **THEN** `main.py` SHALL execute `Plugin(DifyPluginEnv(MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120)).run()` until the host stops it\n75: \n76: ---\n77: \n78: ### AR-036-002: Plugin Manifest Structure\n79: \n80: The system SHALL provide a `manifest.yaml` with all required Dify plugin metadata.\n81: \n82: #### Scenario: AR-036-002-A — Manifest contains required fields\n83: \n84: - **GIVEN** a valid `manifest.yaml` file\n85: - **WHEN** the manifest is parsed by a Dify-compatible toolchain\n86: - **THEN** the manifest SHALL include:\n87:   - `version`: `\"0.0.2\"`\n88:   - `type`: `\"plugin\"`\n89:   - `author`: `\"volcano-sh\"`\n90:   - `name`: `\"agentcube\"`\n91:   - `label`: mapping for `en_US`, `ja_JP`, `zh_Hans`, `pt_BR` to `\"Agentcube\"`\n92:   - `description`: multilingual strings for AgentCube description\n93:   - `icon`: `\"icon.png\"`\n94:   - `icon_dark`: `\"icon-dark.png\"`\n95:   - `resource`: subtree with `memory`, `permission` (including `tool`, `model`, `endpoint`, `app`, `storage` flags and sizes)\n96:   - `plugins.tools`: list containing `provider/agentcube.yaml`\n97:   - `meta`: object with `version`, `arch` (`amd64`, `arm64`), `runner` (`language: python`, `version: \"3.12\"`, `entrypoint: main`), and `minimum_dify_version: null`\n98:   - `created_at`, `privacy`, `repo`, `verified`\n99: \n100: #### Scenario: AR-036-002-B — Tool provider wiring\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 458. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-036: Dify 插件集成 - Delta Specification\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the Dify plugin integration in the AgentCube `integrations` module.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-036\n- **Module**: `integrations`\n- **Language**: Python\n- **Size**: M\n- **Reference Sources**: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/integrations/dify-plugin/`, `/tmp/agentcube-ref/example/pcap-analyzer/`\n\n---\n\n## Files to Add\n\n| Path | Description | Type |\n|------|-------------|------|","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-036/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775879685192,"end":1775879685216}}}}
